本題解析由AI生成：解：選項 \( rac{a}{a-b} -  rac{b}{b-a} =  rac{a}{a-b} +  rac{b}{a-b} =  rac{a+b}{a-b}
eq 1\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{m}{a} -  rac{n}{b} =  rac{mb-na}{ab}
eq  rac{m-n}{a-b}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{b}{a} -  rac{b+1}{a} =  rac{b-(b+1)}{a} =  rac{-1}{a}
eq  rac{1}{a}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{2}{a-b} -  rac{a+b}{(a-b)(a+b)} =  rac{2(a+b)-(a+b)}{(a-b)(a+b)} =  rac{a+b}{(a-b)(a+b)} =  rac{1}{a-b}\)，正確。故選：\( rac{2}{a-b} -  rac{a+b}{(a^2-b^2)} =  rac{1}{a-b}\)。本題考查分式的加減法與因式分解。

本題解析由AI生成：解：選項 \( rac{b}{a} +  rac{b}{c} =  rac{bc+ab}{ac}
eq  rac{2b}{ac}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{1}{2a} +  rac{1}{2b} =  rac{b+a}{2ab}
eq  rac{1}{2(a+b)}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{c}{a} -  rac{c+1}{a} =  rac{c-(c+1)}{a} =  rac{-1}{a}
eq  rac{1}{a}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{1}{a-b} +  rac{1}{b-a} =  rac{1}{a-b} -  rac{1}{a-b} = 0\)，正確。故選：\( rac{1}{a-b} +  rac{1}{b-a} = 0\)。本題考查分式的加減法與約分。

解：選項 \( rac{2}{m} +  rac{1}{-m} =  rac{2}{m} -  rac{1}{m} =  rac{1}{m}
eq  rac{3}{m}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{2}{y+2} -  rac{1+y}{y+2} =  rac{2-(1+y)}{y+2} =  rac{1-y}{y+2}
eq  rac{1+y}{y+2}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{a}{a-b} -  rac{b}{b-a} =  rac{a}{a-b} +  rac{b}{a-b} =  rac{a+b}{a-b}
eq 1\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{a}{(a-b)^2} -  rac{b}{(b-a)^2} =  rac{a}{(a-b)^2} -  rac{b}{-(a-b)^2} =  rac{a+b}{(a-b)^2} =  rac{1}{a-b}\)，正確。故選：\( rac{a}{(a-b)^2} -  rac{b}{(b-a)^2} =  rac{1}{a-b}\)。本題考查分式的減法與分母相反數的處理。

解：選項 \( rac{b}{a} +  rac{c}{a} =  rac{b+c}{a}
eq  rac{b+c}{2a}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{b}{a} +  rac{d}{c} =  rac{bc+ad}{ac}\)，正確；選項 \( rac{b}{a} +  rac{d}{c} =  rac{bd+ac}{ac}
eq  rac{b+d}{a+c}\)，錯誤；選項 \( rac{b}{a} +  rac{c}{d} =  rac{bd+ac}{ad}
eq  rac{bc+ad}{ad}\)，錯誤。故選：\( rac{b}{a} +  rac{d}{c} =  rac{bc+ad}{ac}\)。本題考查分式的加法。
